result.title: Hello my Followers
result.content: Hello my Followers!!! I ve got a surprise just 4 u, I write 2 days earlier than usually bc I miss u so much tht I couldnt wait longer 4 luv i get from u!!! How r u my dear Followers??? Cuz im fine thx 4 asking!! I found a great joke i would like to share with u! A science teacher tells his class, "Oxygen is a must for breathing and life. It was discovered in 1773." A blonde student responds, "Thank God I was born after 1773! Otherwise I would have died without it." Well in fact i dont understand what is funny coz this blonde student was right!!! Stupid teacher!! We cant live without oxygen everybody knows it!! That guy who made this joke was such an ignorant!! Peace n luv XOXOXOXOXOOX
